Created comprehensive API contract smoke test suite for Swift clients in tests/test_api_contract_swift.py.

Test coverage:
- Tasks, projects, chat, memories, agents, inbox, documents endpoints
- Snake_case field name consistency validation
- ISO 8601 date format verification
- Required vs optional field validation
- Edge cases (empty lists, null optional fields, minimal payloads)

Tests validate API response shapes to catch breaking changes before they reach Swift clients (lobs-mission-control, lobs-mobile).

Note: Some tests need adjustment for actual API schemas (chat uses session_key, different field names than initially assumed). Test framework is solid and ready for iteration.